SELECT D_TIME.Month, D_TIME.Year, D_AREA.Province, COUNT(F.NOORDER) AS N
FROM F_ORDER_DEMAND F
INNER JOIN D_TIME ON D_TIME.ID = F.TIME_ID
INNER JOIN D_AREA ON D_AREA.ID = F.AREA_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_TIME.Month, D_TIME.Year, D_AREA.Province)
ORDER BY 
    D_TIME.Year, 
    D_TIME.Month, 
    D_AREA.Province;

SELECT D_TIME.Month, D_TIME.Year, D_AREA.Province, COUNT(F.NOORDER) AS N
FROM F_ORDER_DEMAND F
INNER JOIN D_TIME ON D_TIME.ID = F.TIME_ID
INNER JOIN D_AREA ON D_AREA.ID = F.AREA_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_TIME.Month, D_TIME.Year, D_AREA.Province)
ORDER BY 
    D_TIME.Year, 
    D_TIME.Month, 
    D_AREA.Province;

SELECT D_ORDER_MODE.Type as ORDER_MODE, D_PLACEMENT_MODE.Type as PLACEMENT_MODE, COUNT(F.NOORDER) AS N
FROM F_ORDER_DEMAND F
INNER JOIN D_ORDER_MODE ON D_ORDER_MODE.ID = F.ORDER_MODE_ID
INNER JOIN D_PLACEMENT_MODE ON D_PLACEMENT_MODE.ID = F.PLACEMENT_MODE_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_ORDER_MODE.Type, D_PLACEMENT_MODE.Type)

SELECT D_ORDER_MODE.Type as ORDER_MODE, D_PLACEMENT_MODE.Type as PLACEMENT_MODE, COUNT(F.NOORDER) AS N
FROM F_ORDER_DEMAND F
INNER JOIN D_ORDER_MODE ON D_ORDER_MODE.ID = F.ORDER_MODE_ID
INNER JOIN D_PLACEMENT_MODE ON D_PLACEMENT_MODE.ID = F.PLACEMENT_MODE_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_ORDER_MODE.Type, D_PLACEMENT_MODE.Type)

SELECT 
    DEREF(customerRef).code AS CODE, 
    DEREF(customerRef).name AS NAME, 
    DEREF(customerRef).surname AS SURNAME, 
    DEREF(customerRef).email AS EMAIL, 
    DEREF(customerRef).type AS TYPE, 
    LISTAGG(ACCS.CODE, ', ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY ACCS.CODE) AS ACC_CODES
FROM ACCOUNT ACCS
GROUP BY 
    DEREF(customerRef).code, 
    DEREF(customerRef).name, 
    DEREF(customerRef).surname, 
    DEREF(customerRef).email, 
    DEREF(customerRef).type
ORDER BY DEREF(customerRef).code DESC;

SELECT D_ORGANIZATION.OperationalCenterCode, D_AREA.Province, AVG(F.SCORE) AS S
FROM F_TEAM_SCORE F
INNER JOIN D_ORGANIZATION ON D_ORGANIZATION.ID = F.ORGANIZATION_ID
INNER JOIN D_AREA ON D_AREA.ID = F.AREA_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_ORGANIZATION.OperationalCenterCode, D_AREA.Province);

SELECT D_ORGANIZATION.OperationalCenterCode, D_AREA.Province, AVG(F.SCORE) AS S
FROM F_TEAM_SCORE F
INNER JOIN D_ORGANIZATION ON D_ORGANIZATION.ID = F.ORGANIZATION_ID
INNER JOIN D_AREA ON D_AREA.ID = F.AREA_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_ORGANIZATION.OperationalCenterCode, D_AREA.Province);

SELECT YEAR, OPERATIONALCENTERCODE, N FROM (
SELECT D_TIME.Year, D_ORGANIZATION.OPERATIONALCENTERCODE AS OPERATIONALCENTERCODE, COUNT(F.NOORDER) AS N
FROM F_ORDER_DEMAND F
INNER JOIN D_TIME ON D_TIME.ID = F.TIME_ID
INNER JOIN D_ORGANIZATION ON D_ORGANIZATION.ID = F.ORGANIZATION_ID
WHERE YEAR = 2025 
GROUP BY CUBE(D_TIME.Year, D_ORGANIZATION.OPERATIONALCENTERCODE)
ORDER BY N DESC
) T
WHERE T.OPERATIONALCENTERCODE IS NOT NULL AND T.YEAR IS NOT NULL
FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY;

SELECT YEAR, OPERATIONALCENTERCODE, N FROM (
SELECT D_TIME.Year, D_ORGANIZATION.OPERATIONALCENTERCODE AS OPERATIONALCENTERCODE, COUNT(F.NOORDER) AS N
FROM F_ORDER_DEMAND F
INNER JOIN D_TIME ON D_TIME.ID = F.TIME_ID
INNER JOIN D_ORGANIZATION ON D_ORGANIZATION.ID = F.ORGANIZATION_ID
WHERE YEAR = 2025 
GROUP BY CUBE(D_TIME.Year, D_ORGANIZATION.OPERATIONALCENTERCODE)
ORDER BY N DESC
) T
WHERE T.OPERATIONALCENTERCODE IS NOT NULL AND T.YEAR IS NOT NULL
FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY;

SELECT D_ORGANIZATION.OperationalCenterCode, D_AREA.Province, AVG(F.SCORE) AS S
FROM F_TEAM_SCORE F
INNER JOIN D_ORGANIZATION ON D_ORGANIZATION.ID = F.ORGANIZATION_ID
INNER JOIN D_AREA ON D_AREA.ID = F.AREA_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_ORGANIZATION.OperationalCenterCode, D_AREA.Province);

SELECT D_ORGANIZATION.OperationalCenterCode, D_AREA.Province, AVG(F.SCORE) AS S
FROM F_TEAM_SCORE F
INNER JOIN D_ORGANIZATION ON D_ORGANIZATION.ID = F.ORGANIZATION_ID
INNER JOIN D_AREA ON D_AREA.ID = F.AREA_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_ORGANIZATION.OperationalCenterCode, D_AREA.Province);

SELECT PROVINCE, COUNTRY, N FROM (
SELECT D_AREA.PROVINCE AS PROVINCE, D_AREA.COUNTRY, COUNT(F.NOORDER) AS N
FROM F_ORDER_DEMAND F
INNER JOIN D_TIME ON D_TIME.ID = F.TIME_ID
INNER JOIN D_AREA ON D_AREA.ID = F.AREA_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_AREA.PROVINCE, D_AREA.COUNTRY)
ORDER BY N DESC
) T
WHERE T.PROVINCE IS NOT NULL AND T.COUNTRY IS NOT NULL
FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY;

SELECT PROVINCE, COUNTRY, N FROM (
SELECT D_AREA.PROVINCE AS PROVINCE, D_AREA.COUNTRY, COUNT(F.NOORDER) AS N
FROM F_ORDER_DEMAND F
INNER JOIN D_TIME ON D_TIME.ID = F.TIME_ID
INNER JOIN D_AREA ON D_AREA.ID = F.AREA_ID
GROUP BY CUBE(D_AREA.PROVINCE, D_AREA.COUNTRY)
ORDER BY N DESC
) T
WHERE T.PROVINCE IS NOT NULL AND T.COUNTRY IS NOT NULL
FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY;

SELECT 
    OO.CODE, 
    OO.TYPE, 
    TO_CHAR(OO.CREATION_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm') AS CREATION_DATE, 
    OO.COST, 
    OO.PLACEMENTBY,
    OO.delivery.customerFeedback AS FEEDBACK,
		EXTRACT(DAY FROM OO.delivery.deliveryTime) * 24 + EXTRACT(HOUR FROM OO.delivery.deliveryTime) AS DELIVERY_HOURS
FROM 
    OPERATION_ORDER OO
WHERE 
    DEREF(DEREF(OO.ACCOUNTREF).CUSTOMERREF).CODE = {{Number(tableCustomerAccounts.selectedRow.CODE)}}
ORDER BY 
    CREATION_DATE DESC;

SET teamRef = (SELECT REF(T) FROM TEAM T WHERE T.CODE = {{teamTable.selectedRow.CODE}}),
